{
  "stem": "10283.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If they don't know that I exist, they cannot come for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm not going to register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other lady said, yes, we have to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We have to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they're going to punish us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Most people did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But my mother insisted she was not going to register.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And sure enough, after about six months or so when the-- they-- people that had registered started to get letters that they should present themselves at this and this time at the train station for work-- to go-- to be sent to work.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And a lot of people did, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was the beginning of the deportations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't say deportations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They said, present yourself to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we never got such an letter because they didn't have our address.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course, we could have been caught in other ways because they started to make razias and, you know, to go into the houses and look for Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they closed whole streets on both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everybody on that street had to present their papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, we had a German passport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we had a big J in it, you know, for Jude, for Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the same on trolley cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They closed up trolley cars on both sides and, and inspected everybody that was on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So it wasn't the only way that we could have been caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But it was a big thing that we didn't have-- the register.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] got her letter with the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the boy came running, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Blachmann, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Blachmann, help us!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mother is packing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She wants us to go to the work, you know, to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother ran over and-- over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't live far from us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she lived over a little grocery store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these people were very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, the Belgian people were very good and helpful on the whole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, there were some not, but-- so she had offered to take the girl, who was about 10, to the country and to have her with her relatives, Belgian relatives, and have her live there in kind of hiding.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, you send [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leah ?] to the-- to the country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was, you know, bed and-- like we have here bed and breakfast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You check into a [NON-ENGLISH] under a different name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you stay there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And don't you dare go present yourself to go to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my mother had, in the meantime, found a, a place where she thought we will be hiding.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we heard that-- one night that they were going to come and search the houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So mother and I went into this [NON-ENGLISH], in this little room upstairs and-- to hide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to my mother, you know-- first of all, we didn't have that much money to be able to pay for the rest of the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very-- the people took a lot of money for that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said besides, we're going to go crazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We can't just the two of us sit here for years and, and be hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we came out of hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And she looked for others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had made some other friends,  a Belgian friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was able to connect us with the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with an Underground [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] organization that really smuggled British prisoners of wars out of Germany through Switzerland and through Portugal and back to England.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow, she made a connection there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said, OK, you're the first woman that we do this for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because there were, like here, the coyotes, you know, like people that took people illegally to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was very expensive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, they took thousands of dollars, or franks, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we didn't have that much money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- they gave us false papers like were born in-- we would have been born in Alsace-Lorraine, you know, in, Alsace-- what is it in English?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The border place between France and Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- these people didn't speak French so perfectly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had, like, a German accent like we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it would have been more plausible if we would have been caught that we didn't-- we spoke French by then, but not perfectly and certainly not without an accent.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had these false papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were preparing to leave, like, on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Wednesday before, we got a postcard from my father from Drancy that he's being deported.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
